description.en: WooshCoin (XWO) is a decentralized, peer-to-peer digital currency powered on the Ethereum Blockchain. The creation of WooshCoin (XWO) is to offer a Crypto-Currency coin that can be used every day, safe and securely. The initial purpose of WooshCoin is to provide individuals and businesses with a fast, efficient and decentralized method of making direct transactions while maintaining personal privacy.
